## Installation

Use [`pipx`](https://pypa.github.io/pipx/) to install in a self-contained virtual environment.

```bash
pipx install prosper-bot
```

## Setup

Follow the [setup instructions](https://github.com/grahamtt/prosper-api#setup) for Prosper API

## Running

### Dry run

```bash
prosper-bot --dry-run
```

### For realsies

```bash
prosper-bot
```

